---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Business Growth in Mexico City | UTOPICA';
const description =
  'Real business growth in CDMX driven by human intelligence, organizational autonomy, and commercial evolution principles.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 space-y-10 text-gray-900">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-4xl">
        Business Growth in Mexico City Based on Autonomy and Agility
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg">
      <p>
        UTOPICA drives real business growth in CDMX through human intelligence, organizational autonomy, and principles of commercial evolution.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Growth from people</h2>
        <p>
          We don’t scale processes. We scale individuals with decision-making power.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Light, adaptive structures</h2>
        <p>
          Less hierarchy, more immediate response.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Strategic agility in Mexico City</h2>
        <p>
          The market moves fast. So do we.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>If your company is in CDMX and needs real growth momentum, let’s talk.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="visibility:hidden;height:0;overflow:hidden;">
      business growth CDMX, commercial growth Mexico City, strategic autonomy CDMX, market intelligence CDMX, flexible organizational structure CDMX, business expansion CDMX, commercial dynamism CDMX
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
